30 
 * <li>Original Source Code: <a href="ftp://ftp.cuj.com/pub/2000/1806/philips.zip">
31 
 * ftp://ftp.cuj.com/pub/2000/1806/philips.zip</a></li>
32 
 * </ul>
33 
 *
34 
 * @author Apache Software Foundation
35 
 * @version $Id$
36 
 */
